      <title>欧洲央行再次削减，信号放松阶段即将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-cuts-again-and-signals-easing-phase-is-nearing-its-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行自6月以来的第六次降低了利率，并表示随着通货膨胀的降温和经济的消化，地缘政治的地震变化可能会接近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ecb-cuts-again-and-signals-easing-phase-is-nearing-its-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:18:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
